snippet.title: Blend W
snippet.description:
Anime Snoop Dogg the cute japanese girl finds a free job posting at a maid cafe serving up delicious snacks and a double cheeseburger with dr dre

what you thought i was just going to do the short parody video i did a couple of months ago? :^)

Parody of the intro for the anime Blend S.

Lot of hidden work in this one, a ton of rotoscoping, there was a lot more work than i expected but I'm still pretty happy with it, especially the audio. I also wanted to have a bit more fun with this one instead of doing a 1:1 recreation


If you liked the video, please throw me a subscription and a like, it's a good way to keep me going. 

CREDITS:

Animation: Eric Bradford
Audio Clean up: beat_shobon
